Package: presentresults
Title: Helpers to present results into table or graphs
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
  person("Mehedi", "Khan", email= "mh.khan@reach-initiative.org", role = "aut",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-4276-4485")),
    person("Yann", "Say", "", email = "yann.say@impact-initiatives.org", role = c("aut", "cre"), 
          comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-7390-4209"))
          )
Description: The package provides wrappers to turn results from a long format
    into wide or graphics. It is based on tidyverse mainly.
    For results in a long format, it will work with an analysis key which have 
    the following format: analysis_type @/@ dependent_variable  ~/~ 
    dependent_variable_value @/@ independent_variable ~/~ 
    independent_variable_value
